app.get() (Read / Fetch Data)
📌 Use

👉 Server se data fetch karne ke liye

💻 Example
const express = require('express');
const app = express();

app.get('/', (req, res) => {
    res.send("Home Page");
});

app.listen(3000);
🔍 Line-by-Line
app.get('/') → jab GET request / par aaye
(req, res) → request & response object
res.send() → response bhejta hai
